<td colspan="2"><b>Economic Waves</b> series<br />
<p>(see <a href="/wiki/Business_cycle" title="Business cycle">Business cycles</a>)</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th>Cycle/Wave Name</th>
<th>Years</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Kitchin inventory</td>
<td>3–5</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Juglar fixed investment</td>
<td>7–11</td>
</tr>
